history.content:
So I got waitlisted for some classes but the waitlist positions seem to be different between the enrollment center and the my academics page. For example, it says I'm in position 15 in enrollment center, but the my academics page says I'm in position 19. I thought this was because the academics page hasn't updated yet, but it has been like this for several hours. Does anyone else also have this problem and should I follow the enrollment center waitlist position?

Update: So the my academics page did finally update after several hours. The enrollment center probably has the most up to date info tho
